About

The Citizen Atlas is a powerful story-building website that enables community change makers to inspire action and advance their issues through more substantive, engaging and persuasive data-driven storytelling.

For years, journalists have used a technique known as visual narration to illustrate key facts and bring topics to life. By strategically incorporating a wide range of data visualization elements, including videos, photos, multi-media images, maps, graphs and more into their stories about people, communities, issues and challenges, community stakeholders can make their points in a more substantive, succinct and compelling manner.

The Citizen Atlas provides users with tools, guidance and techniques to develop, build and distribute powerful data-rich stories that blend first-hand knowledge with accessible public data to create visually compelling story-enhancing elements -- such as videos, photos, animation, maps, charts and more – that amplify the impact of their story and inspire others to action.
